        { "type": "heading", "value": "Hero 슬라이더" },
        { "type": "text", "value": "15장의 이미지가 자동 회전하며, 브랜드명 'Miracell'과 슬로건 'Standard of Stem Cell'이 오버레이됩니다. 슬라이더는 풀 와이드(100vw)로 화면 전체를 차지합니다." },
        { "type": "component", "title": "Hero 슬라이더 텍스트 오버레이 (재현)", "html": "<div class='mc-hero'><div class='mc-hero-bg'><div class='mc-hero-grad'></div></div><div class='mc-hero-content'><span class='mc-hero-sub'>STEM CELL SPECIALIST</span><h1 class='mc-hero-title'>Miracell</h1><p class='mc-hero-slogan'>Standard of Stem Cell</p><div class='mc-hero-dots'><span class='mc-dot is-active'></span><span class='mc-dot'></span><span class='mc-dot'></span><span class='mc-dot'></span><span class='mc-dot'></span></div></div></div>", "css": ".mc-hero{position:relative;height:400px;overflow:hidden;border-radius:0}.mc-hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:#0a0a0a}.mc-hero-grad{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(30,10,40,0.8) 0%,rgba(10,10,10,0.6) 50%,rgba(20,5,30,0.7) 100%);animation:mc-bg-shift 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate}.mc-hero-content{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;text-align:center;z-index:2}.mc-hero-sub{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.35em;opacity:0.5;margin-bottom:20px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:400}.mc-hero-title{font-size:56px;font-weight:300;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin:0 0 10px;text-transform:uppercase}.mc-hero-slogan{font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.2em;opacity:0.6;margin:0 0 32px;font-weight:300}.mc-hero-dots{display:flex;gap:8px}.mc-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);transition:background 0.3s}.mc-dot.is-active{background:#fff}@keyframes mc-bg-shift{0%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0.7}100%{opacity:1}}" },
        { "type": "heading", "value": "서비스 섹션" },
        { "type": "text", "value": "3열 카드로 핵심 서비스를 소개합니다. 각 카드는 어두운 세포/DNA 현미경 이미지 배경 위에 흰 텍스트가 오버레이되며, 중앙 카드에는 'VIEW MORE' 텍스트가 회전하는 원형 CTA 버튼이 배치됩니다." },
        { "type": "component", "title": "서비스 3열 카드 (재현)", "html": "<div class='mc-services'><div class='mc-svc-card mc-svc-1'><div class='mc-svc-bg'></div><div class='mc-svc-content'><h3>CellBanking</h3><p>면역세포, 줄기세포<br>추출 보관 서비스</p></div></div><div class='mc-svc-card mc-svc-2'><div class='mc-svc-bg'></div><div class='mc-svc-content'><h3>Stemcell<br>Medical Platform</h3><p>줄기세포 시술 커뮤니티 플랫폼</p></div><div class='mc-svc-cta'><svg class='mc-svc-ring' viewBox='0 0 120 120'><defs><path id='cp' d='M60,60 m-42,0 a42,42 0 1,1 84,0 a42,42 0 1,1 -84,0'/></defs><text><textPath href='#cp'>VIEW MORE · VIEW MORE · VIEW MORE · </textPath></svg><div class='mc-svc-plus'>+</div></div></div><div class='mc-svc-card mc-svc-3'><div class='mc-svc-bg'></div><div class='mc-svc-content'><h3>Medical AICC</h3><p>병원 업무 자동화를 위한<br>Medical AI 콜센터 솔루션</p></div></div></div>", "css": ".mc-services{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:0;border-radius:0;overflow:hidden;height:420px}.mc-svc-card{position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;padding:36px 28px}.mc-svc-bg{position:absolute;inset:0}.mc-svc-1 .mc-svc-bg{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#1a0a2e 0%,#2d1854 40%,#1a0a2e 100%)}.mc-svc-2 .mc-svc-bg{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#1a0826 0%,#3d1560 40%,#2a0d45 100%)}.mc-svc-3 .mc-svc-bg{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#0d0618 0%,#1a0a2e 40%,#0d0618 100%)}.mc-svc-1 .mc-svc-bg::after,.mc-svc-2 .mc-svc-bg::after,.mc-svc-3 .mc-svc-bg::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 60%,rgba(180,100,220,0.12) 0%,transparent 70%)}.mc-svc-content{position:relative;z-index:2;color:#fff}.mc-svc-content h3{font-size:26px;font-weight:800;margin:0 0 8px;line-height:1.3}.mc-svc-content p{font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;opacity:0.6;margin:0}.mc-svc-cta{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);z-index:3;width:110px;height:110px}.mc-svc-ring{width:110px;height:110px;animation:mc-spin 1