        { "type": "heading", "value": "About 섹션 — 통계 카운터" },
        { "type": "text", "value": "스크롤 진입 시 숫자가 0에서 목표값까지 카운트업되는 애니메이션. 기업의 신뢰 수치를 시각적으로 강조합니다." },
        { "type": "component", "title": "카운트업 애니메이션 (재현)", "html": "<div class='mc-about'><div class='mc-about-text'>줄기세포와 세포치료 분야의 전문 기술과<br>임상 경험을 바탕으로 한 바이오 기업입니다.</div><div class='mc-counters'><div class='mc-counter'><span class='mc-counter-num' data-target='2009'>0</span><span class='mc-counter-sfx'>년</span><span class='mc-counter-label'>설립</span></div><div class='mc-counter-sep'></div><div class='mc-counter'><span class='mc-counter-num' data-target='650'>0</span><span class='mc-counter-sfx'>여 개</span><span class='mc-counter-label'>고객 병원</span></div><div class='mc-counter-sep'></div><div class='mc-counter'><span class='mc-counter-num' data-target='23'>0</span><span class='mc-counter-sfx'>건</span><span class='mc-counter-label'>기술 특허</span></div></div></div>", "css": ".mc-about{padding:40px 0;text-align:center}.mc-about-text{font-size:18px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--sm-content-secondary);margin-bottom:40px}.mc-counters{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;gap:0}.mc-counter{text-align:center;padding:0 48px}.mc-counter-num{font-size:52px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1a1a;letter-spacing:-0.03em;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}[data-theme=dark] .mc-counter-num{color:#fff}.mc-counter-sfx{font-size:16px;font-weight:400;color:#888;margin-left:4px}.mc-counter-label{display:block;font-size:14px;color:#999;margin-top:8px;font-weight:400}.mc-counter-sep{width:1px;height:48px;background:#e0e0e0;flex-shrink:0}[data-theme=dark] .mc-counter-sep{background:#333}@media(max-width:600px){.mc-counter{padding:0 24px}.mc-counter-num{font-size:36px}}", "js": "requestAnimationFrame(function(){var nums=document.querySelectorAll('.mc-counter-num[data-target]');nums.forEach(function(el){var target=parseInt(el.dataset.target);var duration=1800;var start=performance.now();function tick(now){var p=Math.min((now-start)/duration,1);var ease=1-Math.pow(1-p,3);el.textContent=Math.floor(target*ease);if(p<1)requestAnimationFrame(tick)}requestAnimationFrame(tick)})})" },
        { "type": "heading", "value": "제품 카드 그리드" },
        { "type": "component", "title": "제품 카드 Hover 인터랙션 (재현)", "html": "<div class='mc-products'><div class='mc-prd'><div class='mc-prd-img mc-prd-img-1'></div><div class='mc-prd-over'><span class='mc-prd-vbtn'>View More</span></div><div class='mc-prd-name'>Smart M-Cell</div></div><div class='mc-prd'><div class='mc-prd-img mc-prd-img-2'></div><div class='mc-prd-over'><span class='mc-prd-vbtn'>View More</span></div><div class='mc-prd-name'>BmSC Kit</div></div><div class='mc-prd'><div class='mc-prd-img mc-prd-img-3'></div><div class='mc-prd-over'><span class='mc-prd-vbtn'>View More</span></div><div class='mc-prd-name'>BSC Kit</div></div><div class='mc-prd'><div class='mc-prd-img mc-prd-img-4'></div><div class='mc-prd-over'><span class='mc-prd-vbtn'>View More</span></div><div class='mc-prd-name'>Chroma M-CELL</div></div><div class='mc-prd'><div class='mc-prd-img mc-prd-img-5'></div><div class='mc-prd-over'><span class='mc-prd-vbtn'>View More</span></div><div class='mc-prd-name'>Vacuum lock</div></div></div>", "css": ".mc-products{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:16px}.mc-prd{position:relative;cursor:pointer;overflow:hidden;border-radius:0;text-align:center}.mc-prd-img{height:180px;transition:transform 0.4s ease;background-size:cover;background-position:center}.mc-prd-img-1{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c4a87a 0%,#8b7355 50%,#a08060 100%)}.mc-prd-img-2{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7a9cc4 0%,#4a6fa5 50%,#5a80b0 100%)}.mc-prd-img-3{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8bc4a0 0%,#5a8b6e 50%,#6b9e80 100%)}.mc-prd-img-4{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b07adc 0%,#7b4ea8 50%,#9060c0 100%)}.mc-prd-img-5{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c49a7a 0%,#8b6b55 50%,#a08060 100%)}.mc-prd-over{position:absolute;inset:0;bottom:auto;height:180px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.65);display:grid;place-items:center;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.35s ease}.mc-prd-vbtn{color:#fff;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.12em;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.6);padding:10px 28px;border-radius:99px;font-weight:500;transition:background 0.2s}.mc-prd-vbtn:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1)}.mc-prd:hover .mc-prd-over{opacity:1}.mc-prd:hover .mc-prd-img{transform:scale(1.08)}.mc-prd-name{padding:14px 0;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a1a;letter-spacing:0.01em}[data-theme=dark] .mc-prd-name{color:#ddd}@media(max-width:600px){.mc-products{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:8px}.mc-prd-img{height:120px}}" },
        { "type": "note", "value": "메인 페이지는 '브랜드 인상 → 비전 → 서비스 → 제품 → 뉴스 → 연락처' 순으로 설계된 전형적인 기업 사이트 스토리 흐름입니다. 카운트업 애니메이션, hover 오버레이, 회전 CTA가 핵심 인터랙션 장치." }
