        { "type": "heading", "value": "연혁 (History)" },
        { "type": "component", "title": "연대별 타임라인 탭 (재현)", "html": "<div class='mc-hist'><div class='mc-hist-hd'><span class='mc-hist-en'>History<span class='mc-hist-dot-top'></span></span><h2 class='mc-hist-ko'>연혁</h2></div><div class='mc-hist-tabs'><button class='mc-htab is-active'>2020's</button><button class='mc-htab'>2010's</button><button class='mc-htab'>2000's</button><button class='mc-htab'>1990's</button><button class='mc-htab'>1980's</button></div><div class='mc-hist-line'></div><div class='mc-hist-body'><div class='mc-decade-hd'><span class='mc-decade-bullet'>•</span><span class='mc-decade-name'>2020's</span></div><div class='mc-yr'><div class='mc-yr-num'>2026</div><ul class='mc-yr-list'><li class='mc-yr-bold'>· 미국 식품의약국 FDA 510(k) '원심분리기+키트' 시스템 전체 승인</li><li>· 허가번호 K250516 - SMART M-CELL PRP Concentration System</li><li>&nbsp; 허가번호 K250518 - SMART M-CELL Bone marrow Concentration System</li></ul></div><div class='mc-yr-sep'></div><div class='mc-yr'><div class='mc-yr-num'>2025</div><ul class='mc-yr-list'><li class='mc-yr-bold'>· 세계 최초 빛 에너지 이용한 링거백 커버 '크로마엠셀' 개발</li><li>· BSC 정맥 주사의 항노화 효과 임상 진행 - 순천향대병원 공동연구</li><li class='mc-yr-bold'>· 발리 의료 특구 줄기세포 클리닉 센터 설립</li><li>· 인도네시아 바이오메디컬특구 줄기세포 치료센터 설립</li><li>· 유럽 재생의학 심포지엄 스마트엠셀 임상 발표</li></ul></div><div class='mc-yr-sep'></div><div class='mc-yr'><div class='mc-yr-num'>2024</div><ul class='mc-yr-list'><li class='mc-yr-bold'>· 글로벌 강소기업 선정 (중소벤처기업부)</li><li>· 보건복지부 장관 표창</li></ul></div></div></div>", "css": ".mc-hist{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Malgun Gothic',sans-serif;background:var(--sm-background-default)}.mc-hist-hd{text-align:center;padding:32px 0 20px}.mc-hist-en{display:inline-block;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#C8102E;letter-spacing:0.04em;position:relative}.mc-hist-dot-top{position:absolute;top:-2px;right:-8px;width:5px;height:5px;background:#C8102E;border-radius:50%}.mc-hist-ko{font-size:48px;font-weight:900;margin:2px 0 0;color:#1a1a1a}[data-theme=dark] .mc-hist-ko{color:#fff}.mc-hist-tabs{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:12px;padding:0 0 28px}.mc-htab{padding:14px 40px;border:0;border-radius:99px;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;background:#f0f0f0;color:#555;letter-spacing:0.01em}[data-theme=dark] .mc-htab{background:#2a2a2a;color:#aaa}.mc-htab.is-active{background:#C8102E;color:#fff}.mc-htab:hover:not(.is-active){background:#e4e4e4}[data-theme=dark] .mc-htab:hover:not(.is-active){background:#333}.mc-hist-line{height:2px;background:#1a1a1a}[data-theme=dark] .mc-hist-line{background:#fff}.mc-hist-body{padding:40px 24px 16px}.mc-decade-hd{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:36px}.mc-decade-bullet{font-size:36px;line-height:1;color:#1a1a1a}[data-theme=dark] .mc-decade-bullet{color:#fff}.mc-decade-name{font-size:44px;font-weight:900;color:#1a1a1a}[data-theme=dark] .mc-decade-name{color:#fff}.mc-yr{display:grid;grid-template-columns:100px 1fr;gap:24px;align-items:start}.mc-yr-num{font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1a1a;text-align:right;padding-top:2px}[data-theme=dark] .mc-yr-num{color:#fff}.mc-yr-list{margin:0;padding:0;list-style:none}.mc-yr-list li{font-size:15px;line-height:2;color:#666}[data-theme=dark] .mc-yr-list li{color:#aaa}.mc-yr-bold{font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a!important}[data-theme=dark] .mc-yr-bold{color:#fff!important}.mc-yr-sep{height:1px;background:#e0e0e0;margin:20px 0}[data-theme=dark] .mc-yr-sep{background:#333}", "js": "document.querySelectorAll('.mc-htab').forEach(function(tab){tab.addEventListener('click',function(){document.querySelectorAll('.mc-htab').forEach(function(t){t.classList.remove('is-active')});tab.classList.add('is-active')})})" },
