        { "type": "component", "title": "게시판 리스트 UI (재현)", "html": "<div class='mc-news'><div class='mc-news-hd'><h3>NEWSROOM</h3></div><div class='mc-news-item'><span class='mc-news-date'>2026.04.06</span><span class='mc-news-badge'>공지</span><span class='mc-news-title'>미라셀(주), 미국 FDA 510(k) '원심분리기+키트' 시스템 전체 승인</span></div><div class='mc-news-item'><span class='mc-news-date'>2026.02.13</span><span class='mc-news-badge'>공지</span><span class='mc-news-title'>[신년인사] 2026년 새해 복 많이 받으세요!</span></div><div class='mc-news-item'><span class='mc-news-date'>2025.08.11</span><span class='mc-news-badge'>보도</span><span class='mc-news-title'>미라셀(주), CGP 아카데미 개최</span></div><div class='mc-news-item'><span class='mc-news-date'>2025.05.20</span><span class='mc-news-badge'>공지</span><span class='mc-news-title'>사우디아라비아 시장 진출 — 현지 파트너십 체결</span></div><div class='mc-news-item'><span class='mc-news-date'>2025.03.15</span><span class='mc-news-badge'>보도</span><span class='mc-news-title'>유럽 재생의학 심포지엄 스마트엠셀 임상 결과 발표</span></div></div><div class='mc-news-paging'><span>◀</span><em>1</em><span>2</span><span>3</span><span>4</span><span>5</span><span>6</span><span>▶</span></div>", "css": ".mc-news{border:0}.mc-news-hd{padding:16px 20px;border-bottom:2px solid #1a1a1a}[data-theme=dark] .mc-news-hd{border-color:#fff}.mc-news-hd h3{margin:0;font-size:14px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:var(--sm-content-primary)}.mc-news-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:16px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--sm-border-subtle);font-size:14px;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.15s}.mc-news-item:hover{background:var(--sm-background-muted)}.mc-news-date{color:#999;font-size:13px;flex-shrink:0;width:88px;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}.mc-news-badge{font-size:11px;padding:3px 10px;border:1px solid var(--sm-border-default);border-radius:99px;color:var(--sm-content-secondary);flex-shrink:0;font-weight:500}.mc-news-title{color:var(--sm-content-primary);font-weight:500;white-space:nowra