        { "type": "component", "title": "주요 텍스트-배경 대비", "html": "<div class='mc-a11y-demo'><div class='mc-a11y-pair'><div class='mc-a11y-sample' style='background:#fff;color:#1a1a1a'>본문 텍스트</div><div class='mc-a11y-info'><strong>15.3 : 1</strong><span class='mc-a11y-pass'>AAA</span></div></div><div class='mc-a11y-pair'><div class='mc-a11y-sample' style='background:#fff;color:#333'>보조 텍스트</div><div class='mc-a11y-info'><strong>12.6 : 1</strong><span class='mc-a11y-pass'>AAA</span></div></div><div class='mc-a11y-pair'><div class='mc-a11y-sample' style='background:#fff;color:#888'>캡션 텍스트</div><div class='mc-a11y-info'><strong>3.5 : 1</strong><span class='mc-a11y-warn'>AA Large</span></div></div><div class='mc-a11y-pair'><div class='mc-a11y-sample' style='background:#1a1a1a;color:#fff'>헤더 (흰 텍스트)</div><div class='mc-a11y-info'><strong>15.3 : 1</strong><span class='mc-a11y-pass'>AAA</span></div></div><div class='mc-a11y-pair'><div class='mc-a11y-sample' style='background:#C8102E;color:#fff'>브랜드 레드</div><div class='mc-a11y-info'><strong>5.6 : 1</strong><span class='mc-a11y-pass'>AA</span></div></div></div>", "css": ".mc-a11y-demo{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}.mc-a11y-pair{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px}.mc-a11y-sample{flex:1;padding:16px 20px;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;border:1px solid var(--sm-border-subtle)}.mc-a11y-info{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-shrink:0;min-width:160px}.mc-a11y-info strong{font-size:14px;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}.mc-a11y-pass{font-size:10px;padding:3px 10px;background:#16A34A;color:#fff;border-radius:99px;font-weight:700}.mc-a11y-warn{font-size:10px;padding:3px 10px;background:#EAB700;color:#1a1a1a;border-radius:99px;font-weight:700}" },
        { "type": "heading", "value": "평가 요약" },
        { "type": "kv", "title": "항목별 평가", "columns": 1, "items": [
          { "label": "시맨틱 HTML ✓", "value": "H1~H6 전 단계 활용. 정보 계층이 마크업에 반영됨" },
